    "data": [
        {
            "title": "萬科尋求推遲兌付第二支境內債券 規模37億元人民幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國萬科提議延遲償還另一只境內債券，表明這家陷入困境的地產<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:開發商;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/開發商\">開發商</a>流動性壓力正在上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據提交給上海清算所的文件，萬科要求債券持有人接受一項允許其推遲兌付12月28日到期、規模37億元人民幣債券的計畫。公司表示，計畫12月22日與債券持有人召開會議討論該提案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">幾天前，信貸和股票市場剛剛因萬科提出展期12月15日到期的20億元人民幣債券而受到衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些展期提議凸顯出公司近幾個月所面臨的不斷加大的財務壓力。萬科是房地產危機中為數不多的未發生違約的主要開發商之一，但到2026年年中將有134億元人民幣債券到期或面臨贖回壓力，公司正承受越來越大的壓力。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7a7d71a6-f29f-389d-8fa7-533bfad0405c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長期以來被視為中國較為健康房地產開發商之一的萬科早些時候曾與銀行進行磋商，試圖獲得一筆短期貸款用於償還12月到期的人民幣債券，但至少被兩家大型本地貸款機構拒絕。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科的債務問題已成為檢驗北京是否會支持疲弱房地產行業的試金石。該開發商最大的國有股東深圳地鐵集團有限公司已提供超過300億元人民幣的股東貸款為其輸血。但深鐵隨後收緊了融資條件，表明在金融支持上的態度有所轉變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Vanke Seeks to Delay Second Onshore Bond as Crisis Deepens</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Li Liu、Foster Wong.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%90%AC%E7%A7%91%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%8E%A8%E9%81%B2%E5%85%8C%E4%BB%98%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%94%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A137%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-150531132.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 23:55:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "強強聯手 網飛將以現金加股票交易收購華納兄弟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 網飛公司(Netflix Inc.)同意收購<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:華納兄弟;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華納兄弟\">華納兄弟</a>探索，促成這場具有歷史意義的合併，使全球領先的付費流媒體服務與好萊塢歷史最悠久、最受尊崇的制片廠之一得以結合。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周五公佈的協議，華納兄弟股東將獲得每股27.75美元的現金及網飛股票。該交易的總股權價值為720億美元，企業價值約為827億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在交易完成前，華納兄弟將完成對CNN、TBS和TNT等有線頻道的計畫分拆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次收購標志著網飛戰略的重大轉變，該公司此前從未進行過如此規模的交易。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-306386b1-8385-30e7-89ce-b2f37763705f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次收購後，網飛將擁有HBO及其熱門劇集庫，包括《黑道家族》和《白蓮花度假村》等作品。華納兄弟的資產還包括其位於加州伯班克的龐大制片廠，以及包含《哈利·波特》和《老友記》在內的海量影視檔案庫。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Netflix to Buy Warner Bros. in $72 Billion Cash, Stock Deal</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Josh Sisco.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B7%E5%BC%B7%E8%81%AF%E6%89%8B-%E7%B6%B2%E9%A3%9B%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%A5%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%8A%A0%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E8%8F%AF%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F-123653605.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 21:15:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普政府示警歐洲：若不改變將面臨文明被抹除的風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Andrew Harnik/Getty Images\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jGka0SxdLlfC_gA9oWSX8w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/04938b0a88f36d73d0f371ec070ea7a1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Andrew Harnik/Getty Images</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 白宮在一份年度國家安全更新中表示，經過數十年的經濟下滑、政治審查和移民潮，歐洲面臨「文明被抹除」的風險。這份報告構成了川普政府對歐洲大陸的又一次尖銳批評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在美國總統唐納德·川普簽署的這份29頁的《國家安全戰略》中，美國政府表示，與糟糕的經濟表現相比，歐洲在文化和政治上的失敗對歐洲大陸的生活方式構成更大威脅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這種經濟下滑與文明被抹除的真實且更嚴峻的前景相比微不足道，」這份報告表示。「如果目前的趨勢持續下去，該大陸將在20年或更短的時間內變得面目全非。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dabc3ea9-266f-3606-a138-1e2d3325f654-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普重返白宮近一年後，美國與其歐洲傳統盟友之間的意識形態分歧日益加劇。白宮抨擊歐盟對美國科技公司的監管，並公開支持歐洲各地的極右翼政黨，還威脅稱若烏克蘭不向俄羅斯做出重大讓步，將切斷對烏援助。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"7月27日，美國總統川普在蘇格蘭與歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩會晤後宣布與歐盟達成貿易協議。圖片來源：Getty Images Europe\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sihq5ku0k5CPBnTeDEXA1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7cba23953ae293e076a17bb20640fb8b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">7月27日，美國總統川普在蘇格蘭與歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩會晤後宣布與歐盟達成貿易協議。圖片來源：Getty Images Europe</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按慣例每年發布的《國家安全戰略》不具有法律效力，但會體現白宮的全球優先事項。拜登政府以及川普第一任期的版本主要聚焦中國及其他美國對手所構成的威脅，而非將矛頭指向美國在歐洲的盟友。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國特使威特科夫曾建議俄羅斯如何向川普推介烏克蘭和平方案 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮發布的這份戰略報告將歐洲的諸多問題歸咎於歐盟本身，稱該集團破壞了政治自由，並未能遏制美國所說的、正在加劇社會緊張局勢的移民潮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Says Europe Risks Being Wiped Away Unless It Changes (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2-%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E5%B0%87%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%B9%E9%99%A4%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-145129319.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 23:55:53",
