            "title": "美國據悉游說歐洲數國 反對歐盟用俄被凍結資產支持對烏貸款的計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Kiel Institute Ukraine Support Tracker\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BdF0OAvJ.7W9ktKEeUWwoQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ab96085361e29d679c687a6ed11e30cd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Kiel Institute Ukraine Support Tracker</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據多位知情的歐洲外交官透露，美國曾游說歐盟內的幾個國家，試圖阻止歐盟動用被凍結的俄羅斯央行資產來支持為烏克蘭提供一項巨額貸款。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些要求匿名的外交官表示，美國官員向歐盟成員國辯稱，這些資產應當被保留以幫助促成基輔與莫斯科之間的和平協議，而不應被用於延長戰爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周歐盟提出一項計畫，擬以被凍結的俄羅斯資產作為支持，為烏克蘭未來兩年的經濟與軍事需求提供一筆900億歐元（1050億美元）的貸款。目前歐盟境內約有2100億歐元的被凍結俄羅斯資產，從2028年起其中更多資產可能被動用。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eff11117-8e6f-3d73-bc32-79ee30512325-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務院新聞辦公室未回應置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">討論發生在對烏克蘭至關重要的時刻。美國正向基輔施壓，要求其同意一項可能不對等的俄烏和平協議。烏克蘭面臨在明年年初耗盡資金的風險，而唐納德·川普政府已切斷大部分對烏援助，使歐洲不得不承擔更大責任。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/y51xvgaTOu.88THccqACUg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2d28f7f74df990a3defc1d40963de251\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Urged Europeans to Oppose EU Plan for Loan to Support Ukraine</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Daniel Hornak、Andrea Dudik.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
